HEADWORD: Incorporated
<hw>In*cor"po*ra`ted</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <sn>1.</sn>
<def>United or combined together to form in one body.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Formed into a corporation and registered with a
government body as such; made a legal entity.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source> <source>+PJC</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Incorporation</ent>⟦br⟧
